title: Raiders fall to Bears on last-seconds FG
text:
Photo: Nam Y. Huh, Associated Press Robbie Gould (9) kicked three field goals on Sunday, including the game-winner from 49 yards out with 2 seconds to play. Robbie Gould (9) kicked three field goals on Sunday, including the...
CHICAGO — Raiders receiver Michael Crabtree didn’t want to talk about lost opportunities after what was just that, a 22-20 loss to the Bears on Sunday on a last-two-seconds field goal.
